# Research Agent — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your keys

# ─── REQUIRED for AI-powered answers ───────────────────────────────────────────
# Get a free API key at https://console.groq.com/
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here

